			<node ID="ID_1448433698" TEXT="popular real-time OS commercially developed by Wind River Systems used in automobile consumer and industrial devices and networking equipment such as switches and routers provide hard real-time support support basic features such as: processes scheduling interrupts interprocess communication" />
