			<node ID="ID_1613530277" TEXT="Start studying Operating Systems Final. Learn vocabulary terms and more with flashcards games and other study tools.  The rate of a periodic task in a hard real-time system is (where p is a period and t is the processing time)  scheduling degenerates to first-come-first-served (FCFS) scheduling if the time quantum is too long. True. A " />
