			<node ID="ID_1374122129" TEXT="What is real-time processing. In real time processing data is processed live (at the same time). In this type of processing the processor needs to be busy all the time. In air ticket reservation real-time processing is used. The ticket is booked online and processor checks whether this seat is already reserved or not." />
			</node>
